      • getPublicDuration

        @Nullable
public java.lang.Long getPublicDuration()
        Duration of the public leg part in milliseconds. This includes individual legs between public legs, but excludes individual legs that lead or trail the trip.
        Returns:
        duration in ms, or null if there are no public legs

      • getNumChanges

        @Nullable
public java.lang.Integer getNumChanges()

        Number of changes on the trip.

        Returns numChanges if it isn't null. Otherwise, it tries to compute the number by counting public legs of the trip. The number of changes for a Trip consisting of only individual Legs is null.

        Returns:
        number of changes on the trip, or null if no public legs are involved
